  <def>BUDDH: through heterodox means of living (often concretely refering to receiving food in an improper way (e.g. by means of work) instead of mendinancy 乞食) (see also 五邪命) (ant. of zhèngmìng 正命); skr. mithyā-ājiva; also 邪命活 pali micchājivena jīvikaṃ kappenti</def>
